OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers with some thunder likely to
OL,7,Fcontinue through the evening, clearing
OL,8,Fthe far north in the early hours.
OL,9,FOtherwise becoming dry with clear
OL,10,Fperiods. Freshening southerly winds in
OL,11,Fthe far west later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMainly dry in the morning
OL,14,Fwith some bright or sunny intervals,
OL,15,Fbut a few showers spreading to the
OL,16,FWestern Isles. Cloudier in the
OL,17,Fafternoon with scattered showers. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
